(% class="box infomessage" %)
(((
**FactHarbor is a Swiss Non-Profit (Verein) governed through code.**
We ensure neutrality by fixing underlying algorithms instead of individual outputs, ensuring every decision is transparent and auditable.

**Project Repository:** [[FactHarbor on GitHub>>https://github.com/robertschaub/FactHarbor]]
)))


